title: Aloo Gobi
ingredients: ['1 tablespoon vegetable oil', '1 teaspoon cumin seeds', '1 teaspoon minced garlic', '1 teaspoon ginger paste', '2 medium potatoes, peeled and cubed', '1/2 teaspoon ground turmeric', '1/2 teaspoon paprika', '1 teaspoon ground cumin', '1/2 teaspoon garam masala', 'salt to taste', '500g cauliflower', '1 teaspoon chopped fresh coriander']
